Start 
  Play button
    Creates and shuffles the deck
      Stack for deck
      Stack for trash
      Shuffle fuction on deck stack
    Creates the peaks
      
      *Use 4 arrays and compare indeces for flipping
    Populates peaks
    Burns one card to trash pile
    Rest sit in deck stack
    
  In play
    Click function
      On card in peak
        Tests if playable
          If playable, plays
          If not, does nothing
      On deck
        Adds card to trash pile
        Becomes active card
    
